H. sikhotealinensis
has a pupa with thoracic horn which tapers towards the top (
Makarchenko & Makarchenko 2009 , Fig. 48
), length 310–320 µm. Abdominal segment VI with 3 pairs of simple lateral setae, segment VIII with 5 pairs of taeniate lateral setae (
Makarchenko & Makarchenko 2009 , Fig. 49
). Mentum of larva with one light-brown or brown median tooth and six pairs of lateral teeth the same colour.
